Class PrideXmlTransformer

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.data.controller.impl.Transformer.PrideXmlTransformer

extends Object
    PrideXmlTransformer contains a list of static methods which convert pride-jaxb objects to pride inspector core objects

      • transformParamGroup

        public static ParamGroup transformParamGroup(uk.ac.ebi.pride.jaxb.model.Param rawParams)
        Transform a paramgroup from pride xml format to core data model format.

        Note: if the paramgroup returned is not null, then it must have a cv param list and a user param list, even they are empty.

        Parameters:
        rawParams - paramgroup in pride xml format.
        Returns:
        ParamGroup paramgroup in core data model format.
